Station Formats
Salem owns and operates 115 radio stations, with 73 stations in the nation's top 25 top markets – and 25 in the top 10.  Salem has strategically focused on the following complementary markets:

Contemporary Christian Music (17 stations)
Christian Teaching and Talk (38 stations)
Conservative News/Talk (33 stations)
Wall Street Business Network (13 stations)
Spanish Language Teaching and Talk - Radio Luz (8 stations)
Other formats (7 stations)
Spanish Christian Contemporary Music (0 stations)
Health and Wellness (2 stations)





